Steps for the project

1. Create new app => rails new re-former
2. Create a User model with the following fields => rails generate model User username:string email:string password:string
3. Migrate a User database => rake db:migrate
4. Add validations to User model =>
    validates :username, presence: true, length: {maximum: 20}
    validates :email, presence: true
    validates :password, presence: true

5. Create :users resources in routes.rb with :only option for :new and :create actions
6. Create UserController => rails generate controller Users
7. Create #new and #create methods in UsersController (empty methods at this step)
8. Create a new view => app/views/users/new.html.erb
